Teresa Marie McEnroe, the daughter of Mr. and Mrs. James E. McEnroe of Towson, Md., was married there yesterday at the Immaculate Conception Roman Catholic Church to Peter John Clare, a son of Mr. and Mrs. John E. Clare 3d of Manhasset, L.I. The Rev. J. Bruce Jarboe officiated.

Mrs. Clare, 24 years old, is a registered nurse at Beth Israel Medical Center in New York. Mr. Clare, 25, is an associate at First City Capital Corporation, a merchant bank in New York. Both are magna cum laude graduates of Georgetown University. The bride's father is a vice president at Merrill Lynch in Baltimore. Her husband's father is president of Panorama Computer Resources, a software-design company in Manhasset.